query:
SELECT tipoServicoCompra, COUNT(*) as total, 
       MIN(numeroCi) as exemplo_ci,
       MIN(mesServico) as exemplo_mes
FROM despesas_v2
GROUP BY tipoServicoCompra
ORDER BY tipoServicoCompra;
